node.text: Finally found #angelhairpasta last weekend and tonight’s #sakuraebi #tobiko #pasta is dedicated to the Chef that does it the best I feel. @edwinyoyogi Ingredients are there but just lacking of something. Maybe it’s the hand that made it. 🤣 Don’t believe, go try it!!! Anyway, dedicated to you guys. #yoyogi #sakuraebipasta @jacquelineyoyogi #stayhomeforsg #homecooked
